## 2. Open Decisions

| # | Decision | Options | Blocking? |
|---|----------|---------|-----------|
| 1 | How many specialist options to present? | 3 options / 5 options / All in-network within radius | Yes |
| 2 | Search radius — how far should the agent look? | 10 miles / 25 miles / Patient's stated preference | Yes |
| 3 | What if no availability within 14 days? | Extend search radius / Show next available regardless / Escalate to human | Yes |
| 4 | Prior authorization threshold — what triggers escalation? | Any auth requirement / Only complex auth / Never — always escalate | Yes |
| 5 | Patient preference weighting — what matters most? | Earliest available / Closest location / Highest rating / Patient chooses | No |
| 6 | Reminder channel — patient preference or system default? | Always ask / Use account preference / Default to SMS | No |

