## 5. Tool Contracts

### `verify_insurance_eligibility`

| Field | Type | Required | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| patient_id | string | Yes | — |
| insurance_id | string | Yes | — |
| specialty_code | string | Yes | Specialty type from referral |
| service_date | date | Yes | Estimated appointment date |

**Returns:** Eligibility status, copay amount, deductible remaining, prior auth required flag

**Latency SLA:** < 5 seconds — required before any specialist search

**Failure mode:** If unavailable → do not proceed to booking; inform patient of eligibility check delay, offer callback within 1 hour

---

### `search_specialists`

| Field | Type | Required | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| specialty_code | string | Yes | From referral |
| patient_zip | string | Yes | — |
| radius_miles | integer | Yes | Default 25 |
| insurance_plan_id | string | Yes | In-network filter |
| accepting_new_patients | boolean | Yes | Default true |
| language_preference | string | No | For language-matched providers |

**Returns:** Array of specialists with name, location, distance, next available slot, patient rating

**Failure mode:** If unavailable → inform patient of directory search delay, offer to send options via patient portal within 2 hours

---

### `book_specialist_appointment`

| Field | Type | Required | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| patient_id | string | Yes | — |
| provider_id | string | Yes | From specialist search |
| appointment_slot_id | string | Yes | From availability response |
| referral_id | string | Yes | Links appointment to referral |
| copay_amount | float | Yes | From eligibility response |
| preparation_instructions | boolean | Yes | Send if available |

**Returns:** Appointment confirmation number, provider address, preparation instructions, copay due at visit

**Idempotent:** No — duplicate prevention enforced at scheduling system level

**Confidence threshold:** ≥ 0.92 — appointment booking triggers clinical workflow; must not book on ambiguous patient confirmation

